The '''Manhattan address algorithm''' refers to the formulas used to estimate the closest east–west cross street for [[building number]]s on north–south avenues in the [[New York City]] borough of [[Manhattan]].<ref>[http://www.ny.com/locator/ Manhattan Address Locator]</ref><ref>[http://www.frommers.com/destinations/newyorkcity/0021020048.html Frommer's New York City 2010]</ref>
